    "And the LORD spake unto <span class=\"person\">Moses</span> after the death of the two sons of <span class=\"person\">Aaron</span>, when they offered before the LORD, and died;",
    "And the LORD said unto <span class=\"person\">Moses</span>, Speak unto <span class=\"person\">Aaron</span> thy brother, that he come not at all times into the holy place within the vail before the mercy seat, which is upon the ark; that he die not: for I will appear in the cloud upon the mercy seat.",
